Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:20.77,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:23.07,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.07,0:00:29.89,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:40.51,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:43.98,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:49.52,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between\Nthe sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:55.74,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:01:02.75,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good\Ntime just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:07.08,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:09.34,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:16.28,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.49,0:01:26.98,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:30.23,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:35.78,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:41.99,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing,\Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:49.04,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave\Nthe rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:53.53,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:55.74,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:02:00.08,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.85,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.87,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:06.62,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:08.19,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:09.85,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.47,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:12.98,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.64,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:15.71,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:19.91,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.20,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.65,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.65,0:02:29.00,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:33.19,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:35.54,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.54,0:02:39.51,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:42.67,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, \Na boy whose body turned to rubber
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become\N the next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.57,0:03:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and\N less able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy was ejected from \Nthe Sabaody Archipelago
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by Bartholomew Kuma, a Warlord of the Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He landed in the female-only \Nempire of Amazon Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Everyone Falls in Love! \NPirate Empress Hancock"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I can't pay you back for \Neverything you've done for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I should be going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men are so mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their arms stretch, they suddenly grow fat,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,their chests are flat,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and between their legs they have...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hate to ask for help again, \Nbut could you take these off?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your family jewels?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I mean these!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to look for my friends now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they'll laugh if they \Nsee me dressed like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it looks very nice on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.65,0:04:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hating frills...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men really are strange creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:04:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for taking it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:05:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never feel relaxed \Nuntil I find my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly are hasty...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as the others are still alive \Nlike I am, that's all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as they're alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can keep fighting again and again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.54,0:05:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna surpass all of those guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.90,0:05:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'm gonna walk on my hands \Nall the way to Sabaody Archipelago!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll make me stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you give me a ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are hasty...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any ships?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Calm Belt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. This maiden island is surrounded
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by a giant Sea King den known as a Calm Belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why sailors never dare come near.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Castaways will sometimes \Nmiraculously drift here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but most of the time only as corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you said there's a pirate group here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Snake Princess's pirate ship, the Yuda,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is pulled by vicious, poisonous sea snakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so Sea Kings can't attack it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the only ship on Amazon Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I build a raft and \Npaddle all the way there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'm gonna build a raft \Nand paddle all the way there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you just thought up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.64,0:06:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrible! It's already about to break!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I thought he was a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no obligation to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are all men unable to swim, \Neven if they're pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only Franky were here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who doesn't know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could've at least escaped \Nto somewhere far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep this up, \NI'll only grow attached to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, now! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.74,0:08:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! These arrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were strong enough \Nto destroy stone walls
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I was being chased earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't seem like \Nspecial arrows, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The arrows possess "Haki"! \NTheir strength is only natural!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haki? What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Margaret is all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man is with her! Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.29,0:08:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:09:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Margaret! Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to hurry and finish the man off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Snake Princess has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have real guts to lay anchor in \Nthe middle of monster-infested waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We were attacked \Nonly moments ago, in fact!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.24,0:09:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sea Prism Stone in this warship \Nmay conceal our presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but staying anchored here for so long
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.06,0:09:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is bound to attract attention visually.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.32,0:09:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not easy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the agreement between \Nthe Kuja and the government
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,forbids us from getting any closer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,than three kilometers from your island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Consequently, we're forced to wait \Nin the middle of the monsters' den.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:09:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say the Kuja are specters \Nthat turn people to stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get real!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you kill that Sea King?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Kings are hardly rare in the Grand Line,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but in the Calm Belts, \Nthey're certainly larger...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no, monstrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any sign of the Kuja ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet, Vice-Admiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no approaching ships at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long is she going to keep us waiting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.69,0:10:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or has the Kuja empress decided to...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sea King!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! Not even cannons have an effect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship'll be smashed to pieces \Nif we don't do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way to defend against it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it planning to eat the entire ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think the very first to greet us \Nis this beast and not the Kuja...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the vice-admiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allowing an entire warship \Nto be food for a Sea King
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.03,0:12:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would belittle the name of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those cuts...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.77,0:12:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you slice it from inside its stomach?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have not come to hunt Sea Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to finish my business here\N and leave these waters quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you have some skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was growing tired of waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last you've returned, Kuja Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Vice-Admiral Momonga \Nof Navy Headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Warlord of the Sea and \NPirate Empress Boa Hancock!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show yourself! I've come for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So sorry, but the\N Snake Princess isn't coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:13:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's sent many replies now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's men for you!\N Such unsophisticated creatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.73,0:13:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen a live man in a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates and merchants always escape \Nby boat when they see the Kuja flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop. That's a crude laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have received her replies of,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I will follow your orders \Nto convene at once."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she shows no indication \Nof coming whatsoever!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This morning's newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A place and date has been decided \Nfor the public execution
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of Portgas D. Ace, 2nd Division \NCommander of the Whitebeard Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no turning back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The World Government has issued strict orders
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,forcing the Seven Warlords \Nof the Sea to assemble!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Refuse and the agreement is off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your title of Warlord of \Nthe Sea will be revoked!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about what that would mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, the World Government \Nhas allowed you to do as you wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but without the title, you would be \Nnothing more than ordinary pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and therefore adversaries of the \NWorld Government and the navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hear that, Boa Hancock?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who placed a kitten...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.26,0:15:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in my path?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.83,0:15:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My deepest apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one responsible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.38,0:15:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've come out, Boa Hancock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're dealing with the boss\N of a bunch of specters!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.11,0:15:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no telling how terrifying she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard--!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's the Pirate Empress?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the definition of the most \Nbeautiful woman in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Halt, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These girls are terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami's much better by far!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.54,0:16:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or not...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One direct hit from these \Narrows and I'm a goner!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that man a gibbon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! We lost him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.59,0:17:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot have a living man \Nin this land whatsoever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to find him and kill him\N as quickly as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.34,0:17:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split up and search!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Find him and \Nkill him, without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a good idea to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.58,0:17:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where I ran from earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No other choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.99,0:17:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't miss this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! He fell into the jungle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:55.26,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000)}"Amazon Lily Empress, \NCaptain of the Kuja Pirates Warlord of the Sea –\N ‘Empress’ Boa Hancock"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:53.92,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've finally come for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.53,0:17:58.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,What meddlesome people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:03.61,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000)}"Youngest of the Gorgon Sisters – \NBoa Marigold"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:03.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My recent replies were lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:08.18,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000)}"Second of the Gorgon Sisters – \NBoa Sandersonia"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:07.32,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not go to war!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to let me keep \Nmy title of Warlord of the Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.41,0:18:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.72,0:18:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also want all of \Nthe cargo on your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What nonsense is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a selfish little child!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you honestly think we'll accept \Nsuch outrageous demands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and haul it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give her anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.11,0:18:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you hauling our cargo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.13,0:18:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to your senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! I blindly listened to what she said!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Portgas D. Ace's public execution \Nis in exactly one week from today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Fist Ace's life will be ended \Nin the town square of Marineford,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.71,0:19:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where Navy Headquarters stands!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, Whitebeard will \Nmake a move within the next week
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to rescue Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navy Headquarters, led by three admirals,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is prepared to counter Whitebeard \Nwith full military force!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.81,0:19:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you lose the title of Warlord, \Nor accept the orders to assemble?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.71,0:19:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decide now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time is nearly up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like the title of Warlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want it taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I hate the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to obey its orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.53,0:19:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does this sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The marines who came to get me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,had a mysterious accident on the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.44,0:19:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and were wiped out when \Nthey all turned to stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's planning to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ship was attacked by the Kuja pirate ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and when it was discovered later,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,only strange statues were found onboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are those?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Strange statues?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.07,0:20:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your childish selfishness \Nwill not be allowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis has a terrible personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.28,0:20:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she gets everything she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.69,0:20:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. There is a reason for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.46,0:20:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because no matter what I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.07,0:20:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even if I kick a kitten...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.03,0:20:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even if I pull your ears off...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.91,0:21:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or even if I kill someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone in the world would forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason for that is, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because I'm beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.71,0:21:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snake Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.80,0:21:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll let you do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.47,0:21:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For being charmed by me, \Nyour guilty consciences...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will turn your bodies solid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love-Love Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanco--!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.85,0:21:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd expect no less from \Na navy vice-admiral...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.58,0:21:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.18,0:22:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You used pain to block out the evil thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.72,0:22:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've much experience, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.34,0:22:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.04,0:22:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could say the same about your men.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.10,0:22:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.85,0:22:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you're the only one left now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.97,0:22:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One and zero are not the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.77,0:22:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will now return to the \Npeaceful Amazon Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.02,0:22:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Snake Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.12,0:22:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boa Hancock!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.23,0:22:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will wait here as long as I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:22:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not return empty-handed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.86,0:23:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do not reappear in two days' time...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.37,0:23:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the agreement is off!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.64,0:23:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoping to borrow a ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.08,0:23:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy makes his way into the Kuja Castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.50,0:23:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but in his rush, he bursts in on \NHancock as she's taking a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.13,0:23:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As he sees Hancock's form through the steam,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.33,0:23:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,something on her back catches Luffy's eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.98,0:23:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.35,0:23:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Secret Hidden on the Backs -- \NLuffy and the Snake Princess Meet"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.27,0:23:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
